hadiths[39]{hadithnumber,text}:
2606,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey jang ( jihad ( karun yahan tak ke wo (لا إله إلا الله) ka iqrar kar lein, phir jab wo uska iqrar kar lein to ab unhoney apney khoon aur apney amwaal ko mujh sey mehfooz kar liya, magar kisi haq key badley padhi. , aur unka (mukammal) hisab to Allah Taala par hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , abu-Saeed aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2607,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui aur aap key baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa bana diye gaey aur Arbon mein jinhen kufr karna tha kufr ka izhar kiya, to umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap logon sey kaisey jang (jihad) karengey jabke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : ''mujhey hukm mila hai ke main logon sey ladun yahan tak ke wo kahin : (لا إله إلا الله) ‏‏‏‏ to jisney (لا إله إلا الله) kaha , usney mujh sey apna maal aur apni jaan mehfooz kar li padhi. , aur uska hisab Allah key zimme hai.'' , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main to har us shakhs key khilaf jihad karunga jo salaat(namaaz) aur zakat mein farq kerega, kyonkey zakat maal ka haq hai, qism Allah ki ! agar unhoney eik rassi bhi deney sey inkar kiya jisey wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko) zakat mein) diya kartey they to main unkey us inkar par bhi un sey jang ( jihad ( karunga. umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : qism Allah ki ! uskey siwa kuchh na tha ke mainey dekha : Allah Taala ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key seeney ko jang key liye khol diya hai aur mainey jaan liya ke yehi haq aur durust hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah Shuaib bin Abi Hamza ney Zohri sey, Zohri ney Ubedullah bin Abdullah sey aur Abdullah ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey riwayat ki hai. 3- Imran bin Qataan ney ye hadees Maamar sey , Maamar ney Zohri sey , Zohri ney Anas bin Malik sey , aur Anas bin Malik ney abu-Bakar sey riwayat ki hai, lekin is hadees (ki sanad) mein ghalati hai. (aur wo ye hai ke) Maamar key wastey sey Imran ki riwayat ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai."
2608,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey logon sey us waqt tak jang kartey rehney ka hukm diya gaya hai jab tak log is baat ki shahadat na deney lagen ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. aur hamarey qibley ki taraf rukh ( kar key ibadat ( na karney lagen. hamara zabiha na khaney lagen aur hamarey tareeqe key mutabiq namaz na padhney lagen. jab wo ye sab kuchh karney lagengey to unka khoon aur unka maal hamarey ooper haram ho jaeyga, magar kisi haq key badley, unhen wo sab kuchh hasil hoga padhi. jo aam musalmanon ko hasil hoga aur un par wohi sab kuchh zimme-daariyan aaid hongi jo aam musalmanon par aaid hongi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Yahya bin Ayub ney Humaid sey aur Humaid ney Anas sey is hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Muaz bin Jabal aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2609,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Islam ki buniyad paanch chizon par rakhi gaee hai : (1) gawahi dena ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Allah key Rasool hain. (2) namaz qaaim karna. (3) zakat dena. (4) Ramzan key rozey rakhna. (5) Baitullah ka Haj karna.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey kaee sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, isi tarah ye hadees kaee sanadon sey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai. 3- is bab mein Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2610,"sab sey pehley jis shakhs ney taqdir key inkar ki baat ki wo Maabad Juhni hai, main aur Humed bin Abdur-Rehman Hameeri dono (safar par) nikley yahan tak ke Madina pahunchey, hamney (aapas mein baat kartey huye) kaha : kaash! hamari Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahaba mein sey kisi shakhs sey mulaqat ho jaey to hum un sey us naey fitney key mutalliq poochhen jo un logon ney paida kiya hai, chunanche (khush-qismati sey) hamari un sey yani Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey ke jab wo masjid sey nikal rahey they, mulaqat ho gaee , phir mainey aur merey sathi ney unhen apney gherey mein ley liya padhi. mainey ye andaza laga kar ke mera sathi baat karney ki zimme-daari aur haq mujhey saunp-dega , arz kiya : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kuchh log hain jo Quran padhtey hain aur Quran mein ghor aur fikr aur talash aur justju (ka daawey ( bhi kartey hain. iskey bawajud wo ye khayal rakhtey hain ke taqdir koi chiz nahin hai, aur Amr (maamla) az sarey nau aur ibtidaai (shuruaati) hai padhi. ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : jab tum un sey milo (aur tumhara unka aamna samna ho ( to unhen bata do ke main un sey bari aur bezar hun aur wo mujh sey bari hain, qism hai us zaat ki jiski qism khata hai Abdullah ! (yani Allah ki) agar un mein sey koi uhad pahad key barabar bhi sona kharch kar daley to jab tak wo achchhi aur buri taqdir par eman nahin ley aata uska ye kharch maqbool na hoga, phir unhoney hadees bayan kerni shuru ki aur kaha : umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas they usi doran eik shakhs aaya jis key kapdey bahut ziyada safed they, uskey baal bahut ziyada kaley they, wo musafir bhi nahin lagta tha aur hum logon mein sey koi usey pehchanta bhi na tha. wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qarib aaya aur apney ghutney aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghutnon sey mila kar beth gaya phir kaha : aey Muhammad ! eman kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''emaan ye hai ke tum Allah par , uskey farishton par , uskey Rasulon par , aakhirat key din par aur achchhi buri taqdir par eman laao.'' is ney ( phir ( puchha : aur Islam kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''is baat ki gawahi dena ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai aur Muhammad Allah key bandey aur uskey Rasool hain, namaz qaaim karna , zakat dena , Baitullah shareef ka Haj karna aur Ramzan key rozey rakhna.''  usney (phir) puchha : ehsan kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''ehsan ye hai ke tum Allah ki ibadat is tarah karo jaise ke tum usey dekh rahey ho, aur agar tum Allah ko dekhney ka tasawwur apney andar paida na kar sako to ye yaqin kar key uski ibadat karo ke wo tumhen dekh raha hai.''  wo shakhs aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key har jawab par kehta jata tha ke aap ney durust farmaya. aur hum is par herat kartey they ke ye kaisa ajeeb aadmi hai ke wo khud hi aap sey poochhta hai aur khud hi aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key jawab ki tasdeeq bhi karta jata hai, usney (phir) puchha : qiyamat kab aayegi? aap ney farmaya : ''jis sey puchha gaya hai, wo poochhney waley sey ziyada nahin janta.''  usney kaha : uski alamat (nishani) kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''us waqt haalat ye honge ke laundi apni maalikin ko janeygi, us waqt tum dekhogey ke nangey pair chalney waley , nangey badan rehney waley , mohtaj bakriyon key charaney waley eik sey badh kar eik oonchi imaraten bananey mein fakhr karney waley hongey.''  umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mujhey us waqia key teen din baad miley to aap ney farmaya : ''Umar ! kya tumhen malum hai ke ye poochhney wala kon tha? wo Jibreel (Alaihissalam) they. tumharey paas tumhen Deen ki buniyaadi baaten sikhaaney aaye they.''"
2611,"Abd Qais ka wafad Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya, unhoney aap sey arz kiya : (aey Allah key Rasool ! ( hamarey aur aap key darmiyan Rabeea ka ye qabila haael (rukawat) hai, hurmat waley mahinon key ilawa mahinon mein hum aap key paas aa nahin saktey padhi. isliye aap hamen kisi aisi chiz ka hukm den jisey hum aap sey ley lein aur jo hamarey peechhey hain unhen bhi hum uski taraf bula saken, aap ney farmaya : ''main tumhen chaar chizon ka hukm deta hun : (1) Allah par eman laney ka, phir aap ney un sey uski tafseer aur tashreeh bayan ki (لا إله إلا الله) aur (محمد رسول الله) ki shahadat dena. (2) namaz qaaim karna. (3) zakat dena. (4) maale-ghanimat mein sey paanchwan hissa (khums) nikalna."
2612,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sabsey ziyada kamil eman wala momin wo hai jo un mein sab sey ziyada achey akhlaq wala ho, aur jo apney baal-bachon par sab sey ziyada meharban ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- aur main nahin janta ke abu-Qulaba ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey suna hai, 3- abu-Qulaba ney Aaisha key razaai bhai Abdullah bin Yazeed key wastey sey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey is hadees key ilawa bhi aur hadisein riwayat ki hain, 4- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Anas bin Malik Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2613,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon key samney khutba diya to is mein aap ney logon ko nasihat ki phir (aurton ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar) farmaya : ''aey aurton ki jamaat! tum sadqa o khairat karti raho kyonkey jahannam mein tumhari hi tadaad ziyada hogi'' padhi. un mein sey eik aurat ney kaha : Allah key Rasool! aisa kyon hoga? aap ney farmaya : ''tumharey bahut ziyada laan-taan karney ki wajeh sey, yani tumhari apney shohron ki nashukri karney key sabab'', aap ney (mazeed) farmaya : ''mainey kisi naqis aql o Deen ko tum aurton sey ziyada aql o samajh rakhney waley mardon par ghalib nahin dekha''. eik aurat ney puchha : unki aql aur unkey Deen ki kami kya hai? aap ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey do aurton ki shahadat ( gawahi (eik mard ki shahadat key barabar hai padhi. , aur tumharey Deen ki kami ye hai ke tumhen haiz ka aariza laahiq hota hai jis sey aurat (har mahiney ( teen chaar din namaz padhney sey ruk jati hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2614,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' eman ki 73 shaakhen (70 darwazey ( hain. sab sey kam tar raastey sey takleef deh chiz ka door kar dena hai, aur sab sey buland « la ilaah illallah » ka kehna hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aisey hi Suhel bin abi Saleh ney Abdullah bin Dinar sey , Abdullah ney abu-Saaleh sey aur abu-Saaleh ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai, 3- Imaara bin Ghaziya ney ye hadees abu-Saaleh sey, abu-Saaleh ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey , aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. aap ney farmaya hai'' eman ki chaunsath shaakhen hain ''."
2615,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik shakhs key paas sey guzrey wo apney bhai ko hayaa (sharam aur pakdamni) ikhtiyar karney par nasihat kar raha tha, is par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (bator takeed) farmaya : ''hayaa eman ka eik hissa hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Ahmed bin Munee ney apni riwayat mein kaha : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik shakhs ko hayaa key barey mein apney bhai ko phitkartey huye suna, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Huraira, abu-Bakra aur abu-Umama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2616,"main eik safar mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath tha, eik din subh key waqt main aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey qarib huwa, hum sab chal rahey they, mainey aap sey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! aap mujhey koi aisa amal bataiye jo mujhey jannat mein ley jaey, aur jahannam sey door rakhey? aap ney farmaya : '' tum ney eik bahut badi baat poochhi hai. aur beshak ye amal us shakhs key liye aasan hai jis key liye Allah aasan kar dey. tum Allah ki ibadat karo aur uska kisi ko shareek na thehraao, namaz qaaim karo, zakat do, Ramzan key rozey rakho, aur baitullah ka Haj karo''. phir aap ney farmaya : '' kya main tumhen bhalai key darwazey (raastey) na bataaun? roza dhaal hai, sadqa gunah ko aisey bujha deta hai jis tarah pani aag ko bujhata hai, aur aadhi raat key waqt aadmi ka namaz ( tahajjud) padhna'', phir aap ney aayat « تتجافى جنوبهم an المضاجع » ki tilawat « يعملون » tak farmaai, aap ney phir farmaya : '' kya main tumhen Deen ki asal, uska sutoon aur uski choti na bata dun? ''main ney kaha : kyon nahin ? Allah key Rasool ( zarur bataiye (aap ney farmaya : '' Deen ki asal Islam hai padhi. aur uska sutoon (umood) namaz hai aur uski choti jihad hai''. phir aap ney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen un tamam baaton ka jis chiz par daromadar hai wo na bata dun?'' mainey kaha : ji haan , Allah key Nabi ! phir aap ney apni zaban pakdi, aur farmaya : ''sey apney qabu mein rakho'' , mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! kya hum jo kuch boltey hain is par pakdey jaeyngey? aap ney farmaya : '' tumhari maa tum par roey , Muaz ! log apni zabanon ki bad-bad hi ki wajeh sey to ondhey munh ya nathnon key bal jahannam mein daley jaeyngey? ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2617,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum kisi shakhs ko masjid mein pabandi sey aatey jatey dekho to uskey eman ki gawahi do. isliye ke Allah Taala ney farmaya : (إنما يعمر مساجد الله من آمن بالله واليوم الآخر وأقام الصلاة وآتى الزكاة) '' Allah ki masjidon ko to wo log abad kartey hain jo Allah par aur qiyamat key din par eman rakhtey hain, namazon key pabandi kartey hain, zakat detey hain, Allah key siwa kisi sey nahi dartey , tawaqqo hai ke yehi log yaqinan hidayat yafta hain'' ( Sura Tauba : 18) ''."
2618,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kufr aur eman key darmiyan farq karney wali chiz namaz ka tarak karna hai'' padhi. .
2619,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bandey aur shirk ya bandey aur kufr key darmiyan farq karney wali chiz namaz ka chhod dena hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2620,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' bandey aur kufr key darmiyan farq karney wali chiz namaz ka chhod dena hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2621,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' hamarey aur munafiq key darmiyan namaz ka muahida hai padhi. to jisney namaz chhod di usney kufr kya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2622,"Sahaba kiram ( (Raziallauh anhum) ( namaz key siwa kisi amal key chhod deney ko kufr nahin samajhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mainey abu-Musab Madni ko kehtey huye suna ke jo ye kahey ke eman sirf qol (yani zaban sey iqrar kerney) ka naam hai us sey tauba karaai jaeygi, agar usney tauba kar li to theek , warna uski gardan maar di jaeygi."
2623,unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''jo shakhs Allah key rab honey Islam key Deen honey aur Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Nabi honey par razi (aur khush ( huwa usney eman ka maza paa liya '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2624,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis mein teen khaslatein hongi usey unkey zariey eman ki halaawat mil kar rahegi . (1) jis key nazdik Allah aur uska Rasool sab sey ziyada mehbub hon (2) wo jis kisi sey bhi mohabbat karey to sirf Allah ki raza key liye karey , (3) kufr sey Allah ki taraf sey milney wali najat key baad kufr ki taraf lotna is tarah napasand karey jis tarah aag mein girna napasand karta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Qatada ney bhi ye hadees Anas key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
2625,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab zina karney wala zina karta hai to zina key waqt uska eman nahin rehta padhi. aur jab chori karney wala chori karta hai to chori key waqt uska eman nahin rehta , lekin uskey baad bhi tauba ka darwaza khula huwa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Aaisha aur Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey eik aur hadees marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab aadmi zina karta hai to eman uskey andar sey nikal kar uskey sar key ooper chhatri jaisa (muallaq) ho jata hai, aur jab us (ghinoney) kaam sey farigh ho jata hai to eman uskey paas lot aata hai''. abu Jaafar Muhammad bin Ali (us mamley mein) kehtey hain : jab wo aisi harkat karta hai to eman sey nikal kar sirf Muslim reh jata hai. Ali ibne-Abi Talib , Ubada bin Samit aur Khuzaima bin Sabit sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney zina aur chori key silsiley mein farmaya : '' agar koi shakhs is tarah key kisi gunah ko kar ley aur is par had jari kar di jaey to ye ( had ka ijra) uskey gunah ka kaffara ho jaeyga. aur jis shakhs sey is silsiley mein koi gunah sarzad ho gaya phir Allah ney uski parda poshi kar di to wo Allah ki mashiyat par munhasir hai agar wo chahey to usey qiyamat key din azab dey aur chahey to usey maaf kar dey ''."
2626,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney koi jurm kya aur usey uskey jurm ki saza duniya mein mil gaee to Allah us sey kahin ziyada insaf pasand hai ke wo apney bandey ko aakhirat mein dobara saza dey aur jisney koi gunah kya aur Allah ney uski parda poshi kar di aur us sey darguzar kar diya to Allah ka karam us sey kahin badh kar hai ke wo bandey sey is baat par dobara muaakhza karey jisey wo pehley maaf kar chuka hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- yehi ehle-ilm ka qol hai. ham kisi shakhs ko nahin jantey jisney zina kar bethney, chori kar dalney aur sharab pi leney waley ko kafir gardana ho."
2627,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' musalman ( kamil ( wo hai jiski zaban aur haath ( key shar ( sey doosrey musalman mehfooz rahen , aur momin ( kamil ( wo hai jis sey log apni janon aur apney maalon ko mehfooz samjhen''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir, abu-Musa aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey) bhi) ahadees aai hain, 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke aap sey puchha gaya : sab sey behtar musalman kon hai? aap ney farmaya : '' jiski zaban aur haath sey musalman mehfooz rahen''."
2628,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya ke musalmanon mein kon sa musalman sabsey behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : '' wo musalman jiski zaban aur haath ( key shar ( sey musalman mehfooz rahen ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees abu-Musa Ash-ari ki riwayat sey jisey wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain sahih gharib Hasan hai.
2629,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Islam ajnabi haalat mein shuru huwa , anqarib phir ajnabi bin jaeyga, lihaza aisey waqt mein is par qaaim rehney waley ajnabiyon key liye khushkhabri o Mubarakbaadi hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad, ibne-Umar, Jabir, aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- mein is hadees ko sirf Hafs bin Ghiyas ki riwayat sey jisey wo Aamash key wastey sey riwayat kartey hain, janta hun, 4- Abul-Ehwas ka naam Auf bin Malik bin Nazla Jashmi hai, 5- abu-Hafs is hadees ki riwayat mein munfarid hain."
2630,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' (eik waqt aayega ke) deene-Islam Hijaaz mein simat kar reh jaeyga jis tarah ke sanp apney surakh mein simat kar beth jata hai. aur yaqinan Deen Hijaaz mein aa kar aisey hi mehfooz ho jaeyga jis tarah pahadi bakri pahadi ki choti par chadh kar mehfooz ho jati hai, Deen ajnabi haalat mein aaya aur wo phir ajnabi haalat mein jaeyga, khushkhabri aur Mubarakbaadi hai aisey gumnam musleheen key liye jo merey baad meri sunnat mein logon ki paida karda kharabiyon aur buraiyon ki islah kartey hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2631,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey usi jaisi hadees marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai.
2632,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' chaar khaslatein jis shakhs mein hongi wo ( mukammal ( munafiq hoga . aur jis mein un mein sey koi eik khaslat hogi, is mein nifaq ki eik khaslat hogi yahan tak ke wo usey chhod dey : wo jab baat karey to jhoot boley , jab wada karey to wada khilafi karey , jab jhagda karey to gaaliyan bakey aur jab muahida karey to bewafai kerey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2633,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab aadmi kisi sey wada karey aur uski niyat ye ho ke wo apna wada pura kerega lekin wo ( kisi uzr o majburi sey) pura na kar saka to is par koi gunah nahin '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- uski asnaad qawi nahin hai, 3- Ali bin Abdul-Aalaa Suqa hain, Abu-Noman aur Abu-Waqas ghair maroof hain aur dono hi majhool Raavi hain."
2634,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''musalman ka apney kisi musalman bhai sey jang karna kufr hai aur us sey gaali galoch karna fisq hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Abdullah bin Masood sey kaee sanadon sey aai hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad aur Abdullah bin Mughaffal Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2635,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''musalman ko gaali galoch dena fisq hai, aur ussey jang karna kufr hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- hadees key alfaz « قتاله كفر » ka maana o murad ye hai ke Aswad Ansaa key Islam sey phir jana kufr jaisa kufr nahin hai aur uski daleel Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wo hadees hai jis mein aap ney farmaya hai ke agar kisi shakhs ko jaan-bojh kar qatl kar diya gaya ho to us maqtool key wali-warison ko ikhtiyar hasil hoga ke wo chahen to maqtool key qatil ko qisaas mein qatl kar den aur chahen to usey maaf kar den aur chhod den . agar ye qatl kufr ( haqeeqi ( key darja mein hota to phir qatil ka qatl wajib ho jata, 4- ibne-Abbas , Taaus, Ata aur doosrey bahut sey ehle-ilm sey marvi hai, wo kehtey hain : ye kufr to hai lekin kamtar darjey ka kufr hai, ye fisq to hai lekin chhotey darjey ka fisq hai."
2636,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' banda jis chiz ka Malik na ho us chiz ki nazar maan ley to us nazar ka pura karna wajib nahin padhi. , momin par lanat bhejney wala gunah mein uskey qatil ki maanind hai aur jo shakhs kisi momin ko kafir thehraey to wo wesa hi bura hai jaisey us momin ka qatil , aur jisney apney aap ko kisi chiz sey qatl kar dala , to Allah Taala usey qiyamat key din usi chiz sey azab dega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2637,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar kisi ney apney musalman bhai ko kafir kaha to un dono mein sey eik ney ( goya ke) apney kafir honey ka iqrar kar liya '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. - « baa » , padhi. « أقر » key maana mein hai, yani iqrar kya."
2638,"mein Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) key paas us waqt gaya jab wo maut ki haalat mein they, main ( unhen dekh kar) ro pada , unhoney kaha : thehro-thehro, rotey kyon ho? qism Allah ki ! agar mujh sey gawahi talab ki gaee to main ( aakhirat mein) tumharey eman ki gawahi dunga, aur agar mujhey shafaat ka moqey diya gaya to main tumhari sifarish zarur karunga aur agar mujhey kuch istataat nasib hui to main tumhen zarur faeyda pahunchaaunga. phir unhoney kaha : qism Allah ki ! koi aisi hadees nahin hai jisey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna ho aur us main tum logon key liye khair ho magar mainey usey tum logon sey bayan na kar diya ho, siwaye eik hadees key aur aaj mein isey bhi tum logon sey bayan kiye dey raha hun jabke meri maut qarib aa chuki hai, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : '' jo gawahi dey ke koi mabood ( bar-haq ( nahin siwaye Allah key aur gawahi dey ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( Allah key Rasool hain to Allah is par aag ko haram kar dega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- mainey ibne-Abi umr ko kehtey huye suna ke ibn Uena kehtey they ke Muhammad bin Ajlan Suqa aadmi hain aur hadees mein maamoon (qabil aitimaad) hain. 3- Sunabihi sey murad Abdur-Rehman bin aseela abu-Adbullah hain ( abu-Adbullah kunniyat hai) , 4- is bab mein abu-Bakar , umr , Usman , Ali , Talha , Jabir , ibne-Umar , aur Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 5- Zohri sey marvi hai ke un sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key farman : (من قال لا إله إلا الله دخل الجنة) '' jisney (لا إله إلا الله) kaha wo jannat mein dakhil hoga '' key mutalliq puchha gaya (ke uska matlab kya hai? ( to unhoney kaha : ye shuru Islam ki baat hai jabke faraaiz aur Amr o nahi key ehkam nahin aaye they, 6- baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik is hadees ki taujeeh ye hai ke tohid waley (har haal mein) jannat mein jaeyngey agar-che unhen unkey gunahon ki wajeh sey aag ki saza sey bhi kyon na do-chaar hona padey, kyonkey wo jahannam mein hamesha nahin rahengey, 7- Abdullah bin Masood , Abu-Zar , Imran bin Husain , Jabir bin Abdullah , ibne-Abbas , abu Saeed Khudri , Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' anqarib aisa hoga ke tohid key qaaileen ki eik jamaat jahannam sey niklegi aur jannat mein dakhil hogi'', aisa hi Saeed bin Juber Ibrahim Nakhai aur doosrey bahut sey Tabe-een sey marvi hai, ye log aayat (ربما يود الذين كفروا لو كانوا مسلمين) '' wo bhi waqt hoga ke kafir apney musalman honey ki aarzu kerengey '' ( al-Hijr : padhi. ( , ki tafseer mein bayan kartey hain ke jab tohid waley jahannam sey nikaaley aur jannat mein dakhil kiye jaeyngey to kafir log aarzu kerengey aey kaash! ! wo bhi musalman hotey ."
2639,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala qiyamat key din meri ummat key eik shakhs ko chhaant kar nikalega aur sarey logon key samney layega aur uskey samney ( uskey gunahon key ( ninnanwey daftar phelaey jaeyngey, har daftar hadey-nigah tak hoga, phir Allah azz-w-jall puchega : kya to is mein sey kisi chiz ka inkar karta hai? kya tum par merey muhafiz kaatibon ney zulm kya hai? wo kaheyga : nahin aey merey rab ! phir Allah kaheyga : kya terey paas koi uzr hai? to wo kaheyga : nahin, aey merey rab ! Allah kaheyga ( koi baat nahin ( teri eik neki merey paas hai. aaj key din tujh par koi zulm ( o ziyadti ( na hogi , phir eik parcha nikala jaeyga jis par (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله) ''main gawahi deta hun ke koi maboode-bar-haq nahin siwaye Allah Taala key aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain'' likha hoga۔ Allah farmaeyga : jaao apney aamal key wazan key moqey par) kaantay par) mojud raho , wo kaheyga : aey merey rab ! un daftaron key samney ye parcha kya haisiyat rakhta hai? Allah farmaeyga : tumharey sath ziyadti na hogi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( ney farmaya : phir wo tamam daftar ( rajister (eik paldey mein rakh diye jaeyngey aur wo parcha doosrey paldey mein , phir wo sarey daftar uth jaeyngey, aur parcha bhari hoga. (aur sachi baat ye hai ke) Allah key naam key sath (yani uskey muqabley mein) jab koi chiz toli jaeygi, to wo chiz us sey bhari Sabit nahin ho sakti ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2640,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''yahud ikahattar ya 72 firqon mein bat gaey aur Nasara bhi isi tarah bat gaey aur meri ummat 73 firqon mein bat jaeygi '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad , Abdullah bin Amr , aur Auf bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2641,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat key sath hu-bahu wohi soorate-haal pesh aayegi jo Bani-Israel key sath pesh aa chuki hai, (yani mumasilat mein dono barabar hongey) yahan tak ke un mein sey kisi ney agar apni maa key sath ealaaniya zina kya hoga to meri ummat mein bhi aisa shakhs hoga jo is ghinoney amal ko karega, Bani-Israel 72 firqon mein bat gaey aur meri ummat 73 firqon mein bat jaeygi, aur eik firqa ko chhod kar baqi sabhi jahannam mein jaeyngey, Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! ye kon si jamaat hogi ? aap ney farmaya : '' ye wo log hongey jo merey aur merey Sahaba key naqshe-qadam par hongey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees jis mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key hadees key muqabley mein kuch ziyada wazahat hai Hasan gharib hai. hum usey is tarah sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2642,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' Allah تبارک o taala ney apni makhluq ko taareeki mein paida kya phir un par apna Noor dala (yani apney Noor ka parto) to jis par ye Noor pad gaya wo hidayat yaab ho gaya aur jis par Noor na pada ( tajawuz kar gaya) to wo gumrah ho gaya, isi liye main kehta hun ke Allah key ilm par (taqdir ka ( qalam khushk ho chuka hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2643,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya tumhen malum hai ke bandon par Allah ka haq kya hai? mainey kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada behtar jantey hain. aap ney farmaya : '' uska haq bandon par ye hai ke bandey uski ibadat karen aur uskey sath kisi ko shareek na thehraeyn ''. ( phir (aap ney kaha : '' kya tum ye bhi jantey ho ke jab log aisa karen to Allah par unka kya haq hai? mainey kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain ''. aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' unka haq Allah par ye hai ke wo unhen azab na dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees mutaaddid sanadon sey Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai."
2644,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' merey paas Jibreel ( (Alaihissalam) ( aaye aur mujhey basharat di ke jo shakhs us haal mein mar gaya ke usney Allah key sath kisi ko shareek nahin thehraya to wo jannat mein jaeyga '' , mainey kaha : agar-che usney zina kya ho aur chori ki ho? aap ney farmaya : '' haan '' , ( agar-che usney zina kya ho aur chori ki ho ( padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Darda sey bhi riwayat hai,"
